parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various safety-critical components to malfunction, such as the horn, airbag, and cruise control, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Horn not working
airbag not functioning
cruise control not working
dashboard lights flickering or shutting off
instrument cluster malfunctioning
and other electrical issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clockspring can cause the airbag, horn, and cruise control to malfunction, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Airbag not functioning
horn not working
cruise control not working
and other electrical issues related to the clockspring.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiring harness can cause various electrical components to malfunction, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Electrical issues
such as flickering lights
instrument cluster malfunctioning
and other electrical problems.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sliding Door and Liftgate Motor Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sliding door and liftgate motor can cause inconvenience and difficulty in opening and closing the doors.
symptoms: Sliding door and liftgate motor failure
difficulty opening and closing doors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition and starting system can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, which can lead to accidents or strand the driver.
symptoms: Vehicle stalling or not starting
difficulty starting the engine
and other ignition-related issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clockspring can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the airbag light illuminating on the dashboard, and in some cases, the airbag may not deploy in the event of a crash, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag light illuminates on the dashboard
the horn does not function
the steering wheel radio controls do not work
the airbag system may not deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly, or not deploy at all in the event of a crash, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag deploys unexpectedly
the airbag does not deploy in the event of a crash
the airbag light illuminates on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent illumination of the airbag light can cause confusion and uncertainty for the driver, which can lead to a delay in seeking repairs, potentially increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag light illuminates intermittently
the airbag light turns on and off while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become stiff or difficult to turn, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels stiff or difficult to turn
the power steering fluid is leaking
the power steering pump is making a whining or grinding noise
the steering wheel is slow to respond
or the vehicle is difficult to steer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The steering column lockup can cause the vehicle to become difficult or impossible to steer, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering wheel locks up or becomes stuck
making it difficult or impossible to turn the wheel
the vehicle is difficult to steer
or the steering wheel is slow to respond.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the suspension system can cause the vehicle to become unstable or difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle is difficult to steer
the vehicle is unstable or wobbly
the suspension is making a knocking or clunking noise
or the vehicle is sagging or leaning to one side.
